ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Exchange of Letters between Canada and the Republic of Columbia
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE, on behalf of Canada the EXCHANGE OF LETTERS between the Government of Canada and the Government of the REPUBLIC OF COLOMBIA in order to amend the FREE TRADE AGREEMENT between Canada and the Republic of Colombia done at Lima on November 21, 2008.
